{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775900332492,"sessionID":"ses_284180dcfffeQWwOBcuErq9vUW","part":{"id":"prt_d7be88d3f001gkkl60MtIIpThw","messageID":"msg_d7be87895001vogKkSs7J2jENx","sessionID":"ses_284180dcfffeQWwOBcuErq9vUW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService and Data Models\n2: \n3: > **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## ST-4.1 — AgentMetadata Model Enhancement\n11: \n12: ### Tasks\n13: \n14: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n15: |---|------|--------------|------|\n16: | 4.1.1 | Add `model_config` to `AgentMetadata` with `populate_by_name=True`, `validate_assignment=True`, `extra='forbid'` | Unit test: extra fields raise ValidationError | 0.5h |\n17: | 4.1.2 | Add field `pack_timestamp: Optional[str]` with description \"ISO timestamp of pack operation\" | Unit test: field serializes/deserializes correctly | 0.5h |\n18: | 4.1.3 | Add field `dockerfile_generated: Optional[bool]` with description \"Whether Dockerfile was generated\" | Unit test: field serializes/deserializes correctly | 0.5h |\n19: | 4.1.4 | Verify `language` validator accepts lowercase/uppercase, rejects invalid values | Unit test: \"Python\"→\"python\", \"invalid\" raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n20: | 4.1.5 | Verify `build_mode` validator accepts lowercase/uppercase, rejects invalid values | Unit test: \"Local\"→\"local\", \"invalid\" raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n21: | 4.1.6 | Verify `port` validator rejects ports outside 1-65535 | Unit test: 0 raises ValueError, 65536 raises ValueError, 8080 passes | 0.5h |\n22: \n23: **Deliverable:** AgentMetadata model fully configured with validation.\n24: \n25: **Files:**\n26: - `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` - AgentMetadata class\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## ST-4.2 — MetadataOptions Dataclass\n31: \n32: ### Tasks\n33: \n34: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n35: |---|------|--------------|------|\n36: | 4.2.1 | Implement `MetadataOptions` dataclass with all fields per design spec | `dataclasses.fields(MetadataOptions)` returns expected fields | 0.5h |\n37: | 4.2.2 | Implement `MetadataOptions.from_options()` class method filtering unknown keys | Unit test: unknown keys ignored, known keys preserved | 0.5h |\n38: | 4.2.3 | Verify all fields have correct default values | Unit test: `MetadataOptions()` has expected defaults | 0.5h |\n39: \n40: **Deliverable:** MetadataOptions dataclass for CLI option handling.\n41: \n42: **Files:**\n43: - `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` - MetadataOptions class\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ## ST-4.3 — MetadataService Core Operations\n48: \n49: ### Tasks\n50: \n51: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n52: |---|------|--------------|------|\n53: | 4.3.1 | Implement `METADATA_FILENAMES` class constant with precedence order | Unit test: constant equals ['agent_metadata.yaml', 'agent.yaml', 'metadata.yaml'] | 0.5h |\n54: | 4.3.2 | Implement `__init__()` with verbose logging setup | Unit test: verbose=True sets DEBUG level | 0.5h |\n55: | 4.3.3 | Implement `load_metadata()` with filename fallback chain | Unit test: finds agent_metadata.yaml before agent.yaml before metadata.yaml | 1h |\n56: | 4.3.4 | Handle missing metadata file by creating default in `load_metadata()` | Unit test: missing file calls `_create_default_metadata()` | 1h |\n57: | 4.3.5 | Implement `save_metadata()` writing to agent_metadata.yaml with correct YAML formatting | Unit test: file created, default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False | 1h |\n58: | 4.3.6 | Implement `save_metadata()` with `exclude_none=True`