| Unit test: returns \"python main.py\" when no files exist | 0.5h |\n95: | 4.5.4 | Implement `_infer_entrypoint()` for Java workspaces returning \"java -jar app.jar\" | Unit test: returns \"java -jar app.jar\" for Java language | 0.5h |\n96: | 4.5.5 | Ensure `_create_default_metadata()` creates valid AgentMetadata with required fields | Unit test: created metadata passes AgentMetadata.model_validate() | 0.5h |\n97: \n98: **Deliverable:** Automatic metadata inference from workspace contents.\n99: \n100: **Files:**\n101: - `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` - helper methods\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ## ST-4.6 — Unit Tests — AgentMetadata Model\n106: \n107: ### Tasks\n108: \n109: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n110: |---|------|--------------|------|\n111: | 4.6.1 | Write test `test_valid_metadata_creation` — create with all required fields | Pass | 0.5h |\n112: | 4.6.2 | Write test `test_language_validation_valid` — python, Python, JAVA | Pass | 0.5h |\n113: | 4.6.3 | Write test `test_language_validation_invalid` — invalid raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n114: | 4.6.4 | Write test `test_build_mode_validation_valid` — local, cloud, Local, Cloud | Pass | 0.5h |\n115: | 4.6.5 | Write test `test_build_mode_validation_invalid` — invalid raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n116: | 4.6.6 | Write test `test_port_validation_valid` — 1, 8080, 65535 | Pass | 0.5h |\n117: | 4.6.7 | Write test `test_port_validation_invalid` — 0, 65536, -1 raise ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n118: | 4.6.8 | Write test `test_serialization_roundtrip` — to dict and back | Pass | 0.5h |\n119: | 4.6.9 | Write test `test_extra_fields_forbidden` — extra field raises ValidationError | Pass | 0.5h |\n120: | 4.6.10 | Write test `test_optional_fields_none` — optional fields can be None | Pass | 0.5h |\n121: \n122: **Deliverable:** Comprehensive unit tests for AgentMetadata.\n123: \n124: **Files:**\n125: - `tests/test_metadata_model.py` - AgentMetadata tests\n126: \n127: ---\n128: \n129: ## ST-4.7 